Peso: 3

Descrição: Candidates should be able to properly maintain a Linux filesystem using system utilities. 
This objective includes manipulating standard filesystems and monitoring SMART devices.

Terms and Utilities:

mkfs (mkfs.*)
mkswap
fsck (fsck.*)
tune2fs, dumpe2fs and debugfs
btrfs, btrfs-convert
xfs_info, xfs_check, xfs_repair, xfsdump and xfsrestore
smartd, smartctl									
